{
  "dialogue": {
    "It's a pleasure to meet you. I'm Harvey, the local doctor.": [
      "Introduction"
    ],
    "I perform regular check-ups and medical procedures for all the residents of Pelican Town. It's rewarding work.": [
      "Introduction_sv1"
    ],
    "I hope you'll find your own work equally rewarding, in time.": [
      "Introduction_sv2"
    ],
    "Oh! Thank you very much! I didn't expect anyone to know it was my birthday today.": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive"
    ],
    "Oh! It's a... well, it's something. I didn't expect anyone to know it was my birthday today.": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative"
    ],
    "You're giving me this? I'm honored. Thank you!": [
      "AcceptGift_StardropTea"
    ],
    "Oh! You... want to dance with me?": ["FlowerDance_Accept"],
    "...Yes. I'd love to!": ["FlowerDance_Accept_sv1"],
    "I brought some medical supplies, just in case. Be careful out there!": [
      "GreenRain"
    ],
    "The first time this happened, we were all worried that the rain might be dangerous.": [
      "GreenRain_2"
    ],
    "But what if it's actually healthy for the body? Who knows... The plants seem to respond well to it, at least.": [
      "GreenRain_2_sv1"
    ],
    "It's for me? Thank you! This will be fantastic drizzled on some pasta.": [
      "AcceptGift_432"
    ],
    "For me? What a gift! This looks fantastic!": ["AcceptGift_348"],
    "You know, on a physiological level, I wouldn't advise the consumption of alcohol...": [
      "AcceptGift_348_sv1"
    ],
    "But there's no denying the benefit of kicking back and enjoying a glass of fine Stardew Valley wine!": [
      "AcceptGift_348_sv2"
    ],
    "I've been working on an 'animal checklist' for a few years now. I want to observe every species living in the valley!": [
      "eventSeen_56_memory_fourweeks"
    ],
    "I tried making my own pickles one time...": [
      "eventSeen_56_memory_twoweeks"
    ],
    "Um, let me put it this way... The frogs we dissected in high school smelled like roses in comparison...": [
      "eventSeen_56_memory_twoweeks_sv1"
    ],
    "As a small town doctor, you can't help but form a personal connection with your patients. That can be both good and bad...": [
      "eventSeen_56"
    ],
    "Well now that you know my secret, I might as well give you an update... I was significantly less winded after aerobics class this week!": [
      "eventSeen_58_memory_oneweek"
    ],
    "I got such a good workout during aerobics class, I think I can treat myself to some pasta primavera tonight...": [
      "eventSeen_58_memory_twoweeks"
    ],
    "I don't know why I was ashamed about being in dance aerobics class. My legs have become so strong, I should feel as bold as a lion!": [
      "eventSeen_58_memory_fourweeks"
    ],
    "I've never told anyone about my airplane hobby before... I guess I just feel comfortable talking to you.": [
      "eventSeen_571102_memory"
    ],
    "As a doctor, you can only do so much to help your patients...": [
      "eventSeen_571102_memory_oneweek"
    ],
    "I've made the mistake of getting too emotionally involved in the past... I won't let that happen again...": [
      "eventSeen_571102_memory_oneweek_sv1"
    ],
    "I've never felt like this before...": ["dating_Harvey"],
    "I've been thinking about you so much, I can hardly do my work.": [
      "dating_Harvey_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "Maru's been unusually cheerful lately... I hear you may have something to do with that.": [
      "dating_Maru_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "Congratulations on your marriage, @. Maru's already informed me that she'll continue to work at the clinic, which is a relief!": [
      "married_Maru"
    ],
    "This is the happiest moment of my life...": ["married_Harvey"],
    "Sunscreen? Check...": ["Resort_Entering"],
    "Sun hat? Check...": ["Resort_Entering_sv1"],
    "If you get burnt, a little aloe vera cream might help soothe the skin.": [
      "Resort_Leaving"
    ],
    "I combed the whole beach for glass. We wouldn't want anyone to get a cut on their foot!": [
      "Resort_Shore"
    ],
    "It's nice to have an opportunity to relax now and then.": ["Resort_Chair"],
    "The trouble is actually letting go of your worries...": [
      "Resort_Chair_sv1"
    ],
    "It's important to stay hydrated in this heat. I'm going to ask Gus if he has any coconut water!": [
      "Resort_Bar"
    ],
    "I'll let you in on a little secret... I can only swim with floaties.": [
      "Resort"
    ],
    "I've been looking forward to it all afternoon! You look radiant in the fresh spring air, my love.": [
      "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse"
    ],
    "Oh! I'm sorry... I, er... have plans to ask someone else.": [
      "FlowerDance_Decline"
    ],
    "I... I can't look at you. Please spare me any more pain.": ["divorced"],
    "...Y...You...?": ["breakUp"],
    "*gulp*... I... I think I'm going to be sick...": ["breakUp_sv1"],
    "I'm busy with my work. I can't speak to you.": ["dumped_Guys"],
    "I want you back in my life, @. I'm willing to forget what happened.": [
      "secondChance_Guys"
    ],
    "We sell a few over-the-counter medicines at the clinic... feel free to stop by if you're feeling exhausted.": [
      "Mon"
    ],
    "I know that being a farmer is pretty tiring work... don't overdo it!": [
      "Mon_sv1"
    ],
    "I feel responsible for the health of this whole community... it's kind of stressful.": [
      "Mon2"
    ],
    "It's a pretty small community, and I'm fortunate to be able to build a good relationship with my patients.": [
      "Mon2_sv1"
    ],
    "I'd like to stay in Stardew Valley for a while. I'm finally starting to feel involved in the community.": [
      "Mon6"
    ],
    "It feels good to know that you're useful.": ["Mon6_sv1"],
    "Oh! Hi, @.": ["Mon10"],
    "Do you... have any medical questions?": ["Mon10_sv1"],
    "Feel free to stop by my office if you're ever feeling ill.": ["Tue"],
    "You're young, though. You'll probably stay healthy without trying.": [
      "Tue_sv1"
    ],
    "Don't overwork yourself, @. Doctor's orders!": [
      "Tue8_query_1",
      "Tue8_query_2"
    ],
    "If our farmers get sick, where will we get our food? We need you!": [
      "Tue8_query_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Your health is important to me.": ["Tue8_query_2_sv1"],
    "I'd like to get to know you better, @. Let's put aside our doctor-patient relationship.": [
      "Wed4"
    ],
    "It's nice to have a friend in town.": ["Wed6"],
    "You have a really healthy glow. That's good.": ["Wed8"],
    "Remember to cover your mouth when you sneeze.": ["Wed"],
    "Then make sure to wash your hands.": ["Wed_sv1"],
    "As a doctor, I'm well aware of the benefits of home-cooked food. But I'm so busy, I have a hard time bringing myself to cook.": [
      "Thu8_query_1"
    ],
    "It's a lot of work, being a doctor. I don't eat as well as I should.": [
      "Thu8_query_2"
    ],
    "If I didn't live alone I think it would be easier.": ["Thu8_query_2_sv1"],
    "Nutrition is important, so make sure and eat well. Try to increase your vegetable intake!": [
      "Thu"
    ],
    "Home-cooked meals are best. Do you cook?": ["Thu_sv1"],
    "It's a beautiful day, isn't it?": ["Fri"],
    "I wish I had less work to do.": ["Fri_sv1"],
    "If you want to hang out in my apartment, that's okay with me. I live above the clinic.": [
      "Fri4"
    ],
    "Stop by my place if you ever need a confidential check-up.": ["Fri10"],
    "Can I do anything for you?": ["Sat"],
    "Take care.": ["Sat_sv1"],
    "I came here because I liked the small-town atmosphere, and the potential for a holistic approach to patient care.": [
      "Sat4"
    ],
    "I've grown to really love it.": ["Sat4_sv1"],
    "*Sigh*... I'm starting to feel kind of old...": ["Sat10"],
    "The older you get the more memories you're burdened with. It can be overwhelming.": [
      "Sat10_sv1"
    ],
    "I think I'll stay younger with you around.": ["Sat10_sv2"],
    "Hmm... I'm struggling to make ends meet. I don't have enough patients.": [
      "Sun"
    ],
    "I guess I should try to get patients from the neighboring towns...": [
      "Sun_sv1"
    ],
    "Imagine having a patient's life completely in your hands, and failing to keep them alive... that's something that will haunt you forever.": [
      "Sun6"
    ],
    "Thanks, @.": ["event_george1"],
    "You see, George, I'm just trying to help you.": ["event_george1_sv1"],
    "*Sigh*": ["event_george2"],
    "Look, George. If you want to behave like this I'm going to have to tell your wife. I don't think she'll be happy.": [
      "event_george2_sv1"
    ],
    "Thanks, @. I appreciate that.": ["event_aerobics1"],
    "*Sigh*... rude.": ["event_aerobics2"],
    "Oh! Hospitals make you nervous, huh?": ["event_heart1"],
    "Just try and relax. I'm here to help.": ["event_heart1_sv1"],
    "Okay. That makes sense.": ["event_heart2"],
    "Um. Okay... If you say so.": ["event_heart3"],
    "...You're right.": ["event_grave1"],
    "...Thanks.": ["event_grave1_sv1"],
    "*sigh*": ["event_grave2"],
    "It's okay to get a moderate amount of sunlight. Just don't get burnt.": [
      "summer_Mon"
    ],
    "Okay. Take care! Stay healthy.": ["summer_Mon_sv1"],
    "Exercise is important, but don't get too exhausted, or you might end up at my clinic!": [
      "summer_Thu"
    ],
    "Make sure and listen to your body.": ["summer_Thu_sv1"],
    "People don't get sick much during the summer. That's nice, but it also means less business for me.": [
      "summer_Fri"
    ],
    "Have you been going into the mines, @?": ["fall_Fri"],
    "It's a dangerous place. I recommend against it.": ["fall_Fri_sv1"],
    "When you eat certain foods you'll perform better.": ["fall_Sat"],
    "Eating a 'Farmer's Lunch' will give you the nutrition you need to water and harvest crops better!": [
      "fall_Sat_sv1"
    ],
    "It's flu season, so you'd better be extra careful.": ["winter_Wed"],
    "Make sure to wash your hands often.": ["winter_Wed_sv1"],
    "I hate to say this, but I do make a lot more money during flu season.": [
      "winter_Sun"
    ],
    "I guess if people stopped getting sick, I'd be out of business.": [
      "winter_Sun_sv1"
    ],
    "Don't get the wrong idea! I want people to be healthy... really!": [
      "winter_Sun_sv2"
    ]
  },
  "marriage_dialogue": {
    "It's a myth that rainy weather causes the flu. However, take care that you don't slip on the mud!": [
      "Rainy_Day_0"
    ],
    "I often worry about you.": ["Rainy_Day_0_sv1"],
    "It was so incredibly lonely living above the clinic by myself... I'm much happier now.": [
      "Rainy_Day_1"
    ],
    "I woke up early, but I made sure not to wake you. You looked so peaceful.": [
      "Rainy_Day_2"
    ],
    "I don't mind the rain. Sure, I can't watch the planes go by, but I can still listen to the radio chatter.": [
      "Rainy_Day_3"
    ],
    "It makes the whole thing a little more mysterious.": ["Rainy_Day_3_sv1"],
    "I have a backlog of house chores I want to complete today. I've got plenty to keep me busy!": [
      "Rainy_Day_4"
    ],
    "How was your day, honey? I was going to do the dishes but I got absorbed in the latest issue of \"Knee Surgery Enthusiast\".": [
      "Rainy_Night_0"
    ],
    "You know, this 'journal of tendon dynamics' is actually bearable when I'm reading out here.": [
      "patio_Harvey"
    ],
    "If you're enjoying life, who cares if it's a little repetitive? That's what I say.": [
      "Rainy_Night_1"
    ],
    "You look a little soggy, hun. Why don't you warm yourself by the fire?": [
      "Rainy_Night_2_male_farmer"
    ],
    "You look a little soggy, dear. Why don't you warm yourself by the fire?": [
      "Rainy_Night_2_female_farmer"
    ],
    "The sound of rain gives our minds something to focus on, so we're not distracted by random thoughts.": [
      "Rainy_Night_3"
    ],
    "That's my theory for why it's so soothing...": ["Rainy_Night_3_sv1"],
    "I made us a nice healthy dinner. Only fresh, wholesome ingredients from the valley!": [
      "Rainy_Night_4"
    ],
    "Just make sure to eat a reasonable portion, dear.": ["Rainy_Night_4_sv1"],
    "I think we're all striving to reach some kind of balance in life. An equilibrium of complexity.": [
      "Indoor_Day_0"
    ],
    "For me, moving here was exactly what my body needed to find that balance.": [
      "Indoor_Day_0_sv1"
    ],
    "Good morning, @! I made you a nutritious breakfast.": ["Indoor_Day_1"],
    "Eggs are a good source of essential nutrients, so eat up.": [
      "Indoor_Day_1_sv1"
    ],
    "I'm going to study the medical literature today. It's important for me to keep up-to-date so I can give my patients the best care possible!": [
      "Indoor_Day_2"
    ],
    "I'm going to listen to some jazz music and finalize my medical reports today. What do you have planned?": [
      "Indoor_Day_3"
    ],
    "I was afraid of you when we first met. It's funny to think about now that we've come so far.": [
      "Indoor_Day_4"
    ],
    "You look exhausted, dear. Let me give you a massage tonight. I promise it will reduce the inflammation in your muscle tissue!": [
      "Indoor_Night_0"
    ],
    "I took it easy today... spent some time reading books, fiddled with my radio, and worked on a model airplane.": [
      "Indoor_Night_1"
    ],
    "It's important to take a day off now and then to relax... stress is unhealthy.": [
      "Indoor_Night_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Good evening... did you finish everything you needed to do today?": [
      "Indoor_Night_2"
    ],
    "Don't worry about me. I'm very self-sufficient. If you have more work to do go right ahead.": [
      "Indoor_Night_2_sv1"
    ],
    "It's stressful to be a doctor, so it's really great to live somewhere as relaxing as %farm Farm.": [
      "Indoor_Night_3"
    ],
    "Oh! I was just daydreaming about the circulatory system and forgot what I was trying to do. It's a classic doctor's problem.": [
      "Indoor_Night_4"
    ],
    "This is a very safe spot. You go on ahead and take care of business, don't worry about me.": [
      "Outdoor_0"
    ],
    "I believe this must be the ideal place to raise children, scientifically. What do you think?": [
      "Outdoor_1"
    ],
    "I may not be the most exciting guy, but I'll stay loyal to you for the rest of my life.": [
      "Outdoor_2"
    ],
    "@... you... you mean the world to me.": ["Outdoor_3"],
    "As a scientist I'm fascinated by the delicate interplay of insect and plant life.": [
      "Outdoor_4"
    ],
    "You and %kid1 are the most important parts of my life.": ["OneKid_0"],
    "Little %kid1 is going to have the perfect childhood here. We're really fortunate to have this opportunity.": [
      "OneKid_1"
    ],
    "So far, I really like being a father!": ["OneKid_3"],
    "I already gave %kid1 and %kid2 their breakfasts. I'm trying to teach them to enjoy healthy food!": [
      "TwoKids_0"
    ],
    "I believe a child should be allowed to play and explore to their heart's content. You're only a kid once.": [
      "TwoKids_1"
    ],
    "Maybe %kid2 will grow up to become a pilot, like I never could?": [
      "TwoKids_2"
    ],
    "My life is devoted to you and the children now, and I'm very happy about it. I always dreamed of having a wonderful family.": [
      "TwoKids_3"
    ],
    "I had nightmares of being a bachelor forever.... I love you so much.": [
      "TwoKids_3_sv1"
    ],
    "@...I still can't believe we're married...": ["Good_0"],
    "You rescued me from a life of loneliness, and filled the emptiness in my heart. Thank you.": [
      "Good_1"
    ],
    "I knew you were the one from the moment you moved here...": [
      "Good_2_male_farmer",
      "Good_2_female_farmer"
    ],
    "Wow, you look really handsome today! Did you shave?": [
      "Good_3_male_farmer"
    ],
    "Oh, my... you look beautiful today.": ["Good_3_female_farmer"],
    "Be careful out there! I have nightmares about your limp body being wheeled into the emergency room.": [
      "Good_6"
    ],
    "I think I'll take a little walk today. I need to unwind.": [
      "funLeave_Harvey"
    ],
    "I had a nice day. It's refreshing to spend some time alone now and then. Did you have a good day, honey?": [
      "funReturn_Harvey"
    ],
    "It's wonderful to see all the plants return to life. The greenery is refreshing after a monochrome winter.": [
      "spring_1"
    ],
    "Oh, it's a festival tomorrow, isn't it? Large crowds, activities... *gulp*": [
      "spring_12"
    ],
    "W...Will you dance with me at the festival tomorrow?": ["spring_23"],
    "It's always a little embarrassing.": ["spring_23_sv1"],
    "Make sure you don't get sunburnt, dear! It's very dangerous for your skin.": [
      "summer_1"
    ],
    "As your husband and doctor, I consider your health and safety my top priority!": [
      "summer_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Have you thought about what you're going to put in the luau soup?": [
      "summer_10"
    ],
    "I would put an item of high value and quality. We all want to leave a great impression on the governor!": [
      "summer_10_sv1"
    ],
    "As summer draws to a close, and the colder season begins, my workload tends to increase. Sorry in advance if I'm a little moody...": [
      "summer_27"
    ],
    "Make sure and diversify your harvests this fall, my dear.": ["fall_1"],
    "Or just grow cranberries... It's really up to you. What do I know?": [
      "fall_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Tomorrow's the fair. The food is very rich and salty, but I'm fine with splurging once in a while.": [
      "fall_15"
    ],
    "I'll admit, the spirit's eve festival usually gives me intestinal pain... but I'll do my best to be brave.": [
      "fall_26"
    ],
    "The air is very dry during winter. That's why our skin tends to become irritated.": [
      "winter_1"
    ],
    "Don't worry, I'll rub a little truffle oil onto your back every night.": [
      "winter_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Are we going to stop by the ice festival tomorrow? I do enjoy the igloos...": [
      "winter_7"
    ],
    "Well, here's to a fantastic year. I have complete confidence that next year will be even better!": [
      "winter_28"
    ]
  },
  "gift_tastes": {
    "It's for me? This is my favorite stuff! It's like you read my mind.": [
      "HarveyGiftTaste_1"
    ],
    "That's such a nice gift. Thank you!": ["HarveyGiftTaste_2"],
    "Hmm... Are you sure this is healthy?": ["HarveyGiftTaste_3"],
    "...I think I'm allergic to this.": ["HarveyGiftTaste_4"],
    "Thanks. That's very kind of you.": ["HarveyGiftTaste_5"]
  },
  "misc": {
    "Movie tickets? Well... yes, I'd love to go with you!": [
      "MovieInvite_Spouse_Harvey"
    ],
    "It's good to do things like this, I don't want married life to get boring for you!": [
      "MovieInvite_Spouse_Harvey_sv1"
    ],
    "I'm nervous about this one... *gulp*": [
      "Harvey_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "I'm scared!": ["Harvey_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie"],
    "Harvey is shaking!": ["Harvey_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie_2"],
    "I have a fear of heights, so those soaring aerial shots really got to me... Still, I had a good time overall.": [
      "Harvey_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "I read a glowing review of this movie in the Zuzu City Times...": [
      "Harvey_love_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "It really makes you think, doesn't it?": ["Harvey_love_DuringMovie"],
    "That was outstanding! I'm really glad that you brought me out for this.": [
      "Harvey_love_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "I don't watch a lot of movies, but this one's been well-received, right?": [
      "Harvey_like_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "That was interesting! I'm going to be thinking about this one for a while.": [
      "Harvey_like_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "This movie seems a little intense for me...": [
      "Harvey_dislike_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "I feel faint...": ["Harvey_dislike_DuringMovie"],
    "*Harvey's blood pressure is skyrocketing!*": [
      "Harvey_dislike_DuringMovie_2"
    ],
    "My body feels inflamed after that movie...": ["Harvey_dislike_AfterMovie"],
    "The movie theater isn't open on festival days!": ["MovieInvite_Festival"],
    "The movie theater is closed for the night...": ["MovieInvite_Closed"],
    "You're the new farmer, aren't you?": ["WipedMemory"],
    "You seem... no. I'm sure we've never met.": ["WipedMemory_sv1"],
    "Hey, @. I'll be working late during the festival, so don't wait up for me at night!": [
      "DesertFestival_Harvey_marriage"
    ],
    "Promise me you'll be careful in the skull caves.": [
      "DesertFestival_Harvey_marriage_sv1"
    ],
    "Going into the caves can be really dangerous. I hope there are no accidents, but still... I'll be here all day just in case.": [
      "DesertFestival_Harvey"
    ],
    "As a doctor, I'd recommend minimizing your exposure to serpent-infested caverns! But ultimately, it's your choice.": [
      "DesertFestival_Harvey_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh, um... these are some model planes I built... do you like them?": [
      "Shop_Harvey"
    ],
    "Hey, @. I'm your secret gift-giver this year.": ["Event_cs_1499"],
    "Here, open it.": ["Event_cs_1499_sv1"],
    "It's not much, but I hope you like it.": ["Event_cs_1500"],
    "Hi. So, I'm your secret gift-giver this year.": ["Event_cs_1501"],
    "Well? Open it!": ["Event_cs_1501_sv1"],
    "It's nothing fancy, but it's the best I could afford.": ["Event_cs_1504"],
    "Oh! So it's you?": ["Event_cs_1801"],
    "Ah... {1} {0}! Thanks.": ["Event_cs_1801_sv1"],
    "Of course I'll dance with you!": ["Event_cs_1632"],
    "You want to be my partner for the flower dance?": ["Event_cs_1634"],
    "Okay. I look forward to it.": ["Event_cs_1633_sv1"],
    "Okay! I'd love to.": ["Event_cs_1634_sv1"],
    "I'm sorry... I already have a partner.": ["Event_cs_1635"],
    "Yes, dear?": ["Event_cs_1736"],
    "...Yes?": ["Event_cs_1738"],
    "The wedding was wonderful... wasn't it, dear?": ["Game1_cs_2782"],
    "Well, we can't forget about the farm... time to get to work.": [
      "Game1_cs_2782_sv1"
    ],
    "Umm... I don't think so.": ["NPC_cs_3956"],
    "Is this a joke? I don't get it.": ["NPC_cs_3957"],
    "...I don't really know you well enough...": ["NPC_cs_3958"],
    "Uh... This is awkward. Look, I don't really know you that well...": [
      "NPC_cs_3959"
    ],
    "Oh? ...Sorry... I'm not ready for that.": ["NPC_cs_3960"],
    "...I didn't know. Uh... Sorry. No.": ["NPC_cs_3961"],
    "...You want to get more serious? I feel the same way.": ["NPC_cs_3963"],
    "I'm kind of nervous. Aren't you?": ["NPC_cs_3963_sv1"],
    "You just got engaged! What are you thinking?": ["NPC_cs_3965"],
    "What? Didn't you just ask someone else to marry you? You're crazy!": [
      "NPC_cs_3966"
    ],
    "Um, aren't you already married?": ["NPC_cs_3967"],
    "You're already married, you weirdo!": ["NPC_cs_3968"],
    "You're strange.": ["NPC_cs_3970"],
    "Heh. Funny joke.": ["NPC_cs_3971"],
    "Oh!! ...": ["NPC_cs_3972"],
    "@... I'm sorry, but no. I won't marry you right now.": ["NPC_cs_3972_sv1"],
    "!! Er... I'm sorry, I don't feel that way about you...": ["NPC_cs_3973"],
    "Look. I already told you no! Leave me alone.": ["NPC_cs_3974"],
    "You already asked me that. What part of 'NO' don't you understand?!": [
      "NPC_cs_3975"
    ],
    "...!!!": ["NPC_cs_3980"],
    "I accept!!": ["NPC_cs_3980_sv1"],
    "I'll set everything up. We'll have the ceremony in 3 days, okay?": [
      "NPC_cs_3980_sv3"
